== Research interests 
Dynamical systems and control theory, with special emphasis on modelling, approximation and robustness of nonlinear systems as well as biological applications.

== About me
I received the Laurea Magistrale degree (cum laude) in [https://lauree.dei.unipd.it/lauree-magistrali/lm-ingegneria-dellautomazione/ Ingegneria dell'Automazione] from the [https://www.unipd.it/ University of Padova] in 2013 and the Ph.D. degree in Control Theory from the [https://www.imperial.ac.uk/electrical-engineering/research/control-and-power/ Control and Power Group] at [https://www.imperial.ac.uk/ Imperial College London] in 2017. I then joined the [http://www-control.eng.cam.ac.uk/ Control Group] and [https://www.sid.cam.ac.uk/people/dr-alberto-padoan Sidney Sussex College] as a Research Associate at the [https://www.cam.ac.uk/ University of Cambridge]. 

